{"tid":2245751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星島：教育局將解散教師中心　教協預首次由非建制贏出的選舉更突被取消","createTime":"2020-10-16T12:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T19:52:59.000Z","uid":22556,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8a5da2fff79bf398188d87c3aaaf9918b11c2f","tid":2245751,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"《星島日報》今日（16 日）引述消息，指教育局以使用率偏低為由，即將關閉位於九龍塘沙福道、擁有 30 年歷史的教師中心。立法會教育界議員、教協副會長葉建源表示，教育局先是在年初執意以疫情為由、延後教師中心諮詢管理委員會（諮委會）選舉 8 個月，再於舉行選舉「死線」前「放料」直接關閉教師中心，認為與非建制候選人在今次諮委會選舉，或有望首次奪得過半數席位有關；葉認為，政府對待此事跟對待立法會、區議會態度相同，「贏唔到就取消選舉」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E5%B1%80%E8%A7%A3%E6%95%A3%E6%95%99%E5%B8%AB%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83-%E6%95%99%E5%8D%94%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E5%8E%9F%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%9B%E5%8B%9D%E5%87%BA%E8%AB%AE%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E8%91%89%E5%BB%BA%E6%BA%90%E8%BD%9F-%E8%B4%8F%E5%94%94%E5%88%B0%E5%B0%B1%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88/?fbclid=IwAR11-d82WJUfx8k3dlweZuGhihZ930LhoKcXyT573gB8fRo0714INWP8RRY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2595%25A3%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583-%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%25E5%258E%259F%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%259C%259B%25E5%258B%259D%25E5%2587%25BA%25E8%25AB%25AE%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E6%25BA%2590%25E8%25BD%259F-%25E8%25B4%258F%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%2588%25B0%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR11-d82WJUfx8k3dlweZuGhihZ930LhoKcXyT573gB8fRo0714INWP8RRY&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a139b7ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2595%2599%25E8%2582%25B2%25E5%25B1%2580%25E8%25A7%25A